      "title": "Separate lane for bicycle users",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo Municipal Council (CMC)today launched a pilot program to allocate a separate lane for bicycle users, as there is a considerable increase in the use of push bicycles due to the current fuel and transport issues.Colombo\u00a0Mayor\u00a0Rosy Senanayake also took part in the event. Pix by Nisal Baduge"
      ],
